# LedgerMind

AI-powered crypto accounting and treasury management platform.

# Overview

LedgerMind helps users track, analyze, and manage blockchain transactions automatically.

The platform provides:

Wallet analytics
Tax reporting
Portfolio tracking
Treasury management
Financial insights

# Features

## Wallet Analytics

Transaction tracking
Profit and loss analysis
Stablecoin reporting
Asset categorization

## Accounting Tools

Tax exports
CSV/PDF reports
Bookkeeping automation
Multi-wallet support

## AI Features

AI transaction categorization
Financial summaries
Fraud detection
Smart insights

# Tech Stack

## Frontend

Next.js
React
TailwindCSS

## Backend

NestJS
PostgreSQL
Prisma
Blockchain
Stellar SDK

# Revenue Model

SaaS subscriptions
Enterprise dashboards
Accounting tools
Reporting APIs

## Users

Traders
